snippet.title: Slitherine Next 2024 | Warhammer 40,000: Battlesector – Developers Talk
snippet.description:
Let’s take a deep dive into the world of Warhammer 40,000: Battlesector, interviewing our developers to discover the latest features of the game.
Slitherine Poland, Volmi, and FutureRats form the perfect team to unleash destruction.

🎮 Play now on Steam ➡️ http://steam.gs/l/54eow
💬 Join the Discord Server ➡️  https://discord.gg/Uc3PmqzcDV
